com.nerjal.json.parser

Class FileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nerjal.json.parser.StringParser
      • com.nerjal.json.parser.FileParser

  • public class FileParser
extends StringParser

    A parser to get a JSON5 structure from a file

    Once initiated, use parse() to parse the file and get the corresponding JsonElement.
    Alternatively, use the static method parse(File) to directly parse a file to the corresponding element.

    Since:
    JDK 16
    Author:
    nerjal
    See Also:
    JsonParser
